 <div class="post-1267 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-ekonews category-events category-rangers" id="post-1267">
 <p class="postmetadataw">Posted by: <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?author=1" title="Posts by admin" rel="author">admin</a> | on February 20, 2013</p>		
 <h2 class="post-title"><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?p=1267">Events and More Events</a></h2>
 <div class="content-ver-sep"> </div>
 <div class="entrytext">
  <p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/love-events-title.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1148" title="love events title" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/love-events-title.png" alt="" width="264" height="90" /></a></p>
<p>We wanted to apologize to the <strong>boys</strong> for giving a floating platform that is TIMED instead of permanent for Valentines Day. If anyone would like to receive a permanent copy of this item, please contact us in Customer Support (the question mark). The permanent copy is for Pioneers only, however, so if you would prefer something else instead, you can choose from one of the following items (ONLY):</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/valentines-item-boys.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1269" title="valentines item  boys" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/valentines-item-boys.png" alt="" width="586" height="123" /></a></p>
<p>Just type in the name of the item you’d like in your support request. Remember, you can either have the floating spaceship (Pioneer) or one of the 3 items shown above.</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/rangers-of-the-week-header.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-14" title="rangers of the week header" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/rangers-of-the-week-header.png" alt="" width="625" height="62" /></a></p>
<p>1stLady made a short visit to ekoloko on Monday and ran into her good friend Ramzanahmed – who because of HIS time zone, could not make it to Sunday&#8217;s Ranger Ceremony! Lucky for Ramzanahmed that 1stLady was there and was able to give him a small but quality Ranger Ceremony and award him his well-deserved Advanced Ranger halo!</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/ramzanahmed_cer.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1270" title="ramzanahmed_cer" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/ramzanahmed_cer.png" alt="" width="446" height="275" /></a></p>
<p>And of course, where would we be without our next group of Rangers of the Week!!!???!!!</p>
<p>So, drumroll please (or as YuvalXD says ‘tam tam tam!’), here they are:</p>
<p>spider5x, Dracula, Bigweevil367, gunr224, Matrok, and elikokiko!</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/group8squad2rangers.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1271" title="group8squad2rangers" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/group8squad2rangers.png" alt="" width="578" height="243" /></a></p>
<p>Your ceremony will be this coming Sunday, February 23<sup>rd</sup>, at 2 PM Eastern Time (again, that’s 8 PM in France and 9 PM in Israel).</p>
<p>Congratulations to all and continue to make us proud!</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/news-title11.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-120" title="news title1" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/news-title11.png" alt="" width="339" height="63" /></a></p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/NinjaLady.png" ><img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-1268" title="NinjaLady" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/NinjaLady.png" alt="" width="146" height="258" /></a>Be on the lookout!!! We have heard rumors that this weekend there will be a Return of the Ninjas! Are you ready to join them?</p>
<p>Dust off your Ninja masks and headbands, get your training shoes on and get ready for some serious Ninja Fun! Log in and get some serious Ninja prizes!</p>
<p>Starting this Friday, February 22<sup>nd</sup>!</p>
 <div class="clear"> </div>
 <div class="up-bottom-border">
 <p class="postmetadata">Posted in <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=3" title="View all posts in EkoNews" rel="category">EkoNews</a>, <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=6" title="View all posts in Events" rel="category">Events</a>, <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=7" title="View all posts in Rangers" rel="category">Rangers</a> |   <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?p=1267#comments" title="Comment on Events and More Events">14 Comments &#187;</a> </p>
 </div>
 </div></div>
 
 <div class="post-1223 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-contests category-ekoart category-events category-rangers" id="post-1223">
 <p class="postmetadataw">Posted by: <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?author=1" title="Posts by admin" rel="author">admin</a> | on February 18, 2013</p>		
 <h2 class="post-title"><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?p=1223">Lovely Houses Lovely Days</a></h2>
 <div class="content-ver-sep"> </div>
 <div class="entrytext">
  <p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/love-events-title.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1148" title="love events title" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/love-events-title.png" alt="" width="264" height="90" /></a></p>
<p>You are not sharing the love hard enough!!!! Come on Ekos! We need you to start jumping faster to collect those hearts, and we need you to continue donating Kokos so those Valentines and Love Letters can be sent to help us share the love!!!</p>
<p>Don’t you want to meet the TARGETS???</p>
<p>We’ve given you two extra days, so come on ekoloko – whose got a little love to share???</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/score.png" ><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1224" title="score" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/score.png" alt="" width="354" height="66" /></a></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>And now…what you have all been waiting for!!! It’s time for the results of our <span style="color: #ff00ff;">LOVELY MOON HOME CONTEST</span>!</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/contests1.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-122" title="contests1" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/contests1.png" alt="" width="312" height="50" /></a></p>
<p>Here they are, the winners of the <span style="color: #ff00ff;">LOVELY MOON HOUSE</span> Valentine’s Day Contest.</p>
<p>So many of you sent in your moon homes and you all did a great job. It was really difficult choosing the winners, and we consulted the biggest minds in the world of design of lovely homes…</p>
<p>In the end we decided to choose 3 winners a day for each day of the official event (Feb. 12-17) and we divided them into different categories – <span style="color: #ff0000;">the top winner in each category will win the top prize</span>, and <span style="color: #ff0000;">all of the others will win the second place prize</span>. So here they are: our top 18 Lovely Moon Homes and the First Place winners in each category! Congratulations to our winners!</p>
<ul>
<li>Best heart creation:</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>First place</strong>: amit5000 (perfect symmetry)</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/amit5000.png" ><img class="alignnone  wp-image-1226" title="amit5000" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/amit5000.png" alt="" width="577" height="359" /></a></p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/KarinaaMOONHouse.jpg" ><img class="alignnone  wp-image-1229" title="KarinaaMOONHouse" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/KarinaaMOONHouse.jpg" alt="" width="650" height="325" /></a></p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/Ekoloko-house-picture-Jessica631.png" ><img class="alignnone  wp-image-1228" title="Ekoloko house picture Jessica631" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/Ekoloko-house-picture-Jessica631.png" alt="" width="578" height="361" /></a></p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/dracula.png" ><img class="alignnone  wp-image-1227" title="dracula" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/dracula.png" alt="" width="514" height="320" /></a></p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/Happy-Valentines-Day-Rotem-Butterfly-2.png" ><img class="alignnone  wp-image-1230" title="Happy Valentine's Day Rotem Butterfly 2" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/Happy-Valentines-Day-Rotem-Butterfly-2.png" alt="" width="509" height="287" /></a></p>
<ul>
<li>Best mixed theme style:</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>First place</strong>: facehole (peace is love)</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/faceholemoon2.jpg" ><img class="alignnone  wp-image-1233" title="faceholemoon2" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/faceholemoon2.jpg" alt="" width="521" height="248" /></a></p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/goldstarnewvalmoon.png" ><img class="alignnone  wp-image-1234" title="goldstarnewvalmoon" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/goldstarnewvalmoon.png" alt="" width="513" height="301" /></a></p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/xtrims-house.png" ><img class="alignnone  wp-image-1236" title="xtrims house" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/xtrims-house.png" alt="" width="519" height="294" /></a></p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/mazaiiiiiiiiiMoon.png" ><img class="alignnone  wp-image-1235" title="mazaiiiiiiiiiMoon" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/mazaiiiiiiiiiMoon.png" alt="" width="522" height="298" /></a></p>
<ul>
<li>Most romantic:</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>First place</strong>: iCandy</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/iCandy.jpg" ><img class="alignnone  wp-image-1240" title="iCandy" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/iCandy.jpg" alt="" width="515" height="294" /></a></p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/cchen222.png" ><img class="alignnone  wp-image-1238" title="cchen222" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/cchen222.png" alt="" width="525" height="263" /></a></p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/Happy-Valentines-Day-2-dancing4lyfe.jpg" ><img class="alignnone  wp-image-1239" title="Happy Valentines Day 2 dancing4lyfe" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/Happy-Valentines-Day-2-dancing4lyfe.jpg" alt="" width="506" height="316" /></a></p>
<ul>
<li>Best message:</li>
</ul>
<p>First place: <strong>Donuts</strong></p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/HOMEdonuts.png" ><img class="alignnone  wp-image-1244" title="HOMEdonuts" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/HOMEdonuts.png" alt="" width="498" height="293" /></a></p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/ofeky123.png" ><img class="alignnone  wp-image-1245" title="ofeky123" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/ofeky123.png" alt="" width="473" height="307" /></a></p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/avriLa2.png" ><img class="alignnone  wp-image-1242" title="avriLa2" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/avriLa2.png" alt="" width="504" height="236" /></a></p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/badUboyMoon.jpg" ><img class="alignnone  wp-image-1243" title="badUboyMoon" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/badUboyMoon.jpg" alt="" width="464" height="252" /></a></p>
<ul>
<li>Best new lovely home:</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>First place</strong>: FionaDawn</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/fionadawnMoon.jpg" ><img class="alignnone  wp-image-1247" title="fionadawnMoon" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/fionadawnMoon.jpg" alt="" width="439" height="242" /></a></p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/guygosh.jpg" ><img class="alignnone  wp-image-1248" title="guygosh" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/guygosh.jpg" alt="" width="473" height="230" /></a></p>
<p>Congratulations again to all our winners!</p>
<p><strong>First prize</strong>: Beating red heart necklace!</p>
<p><strong>Second prize</strong>: Silver key necklace</p>
<p>New contest soon! Get ready for some spring cleaning.</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/rangers-of-the-week-header.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-14" title="rangers of the week header" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/rangers-of-the-week-header.png" alt="" width="625" height="62" /></a></p>
<p>Here are some fun photos of our Ranger ceremonies this week! We held a small separate Ranger Ceremony for Karinaa on Saturday and today’s ceremony included bouba57, in15na, and misheli and then latecomer abdulrehm745!</p>
<p>Not present: Ramzanahmed, vikisosa, childofpira</p>
<p><span style="color: #008000;">IzzyRo will be available to hold Ranger ceremonies today (Monday) at 8 PM EST OR on Wednesday at 8 PM EST. If you can make it at that time – LOG IN to ekoloko, server ONE, and be in the Rainbow Shuttle at 8 PM on either of those days! Don’t be late!</span></p>
<p>Congratulations to our new rangers and continue to make us proud!</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/karinaaCeremony.jpg" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1251" title="karinaaCeremony" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/karinaaCeremony.jpg" alt="" width="389" height="242" /></a></p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/ceremony172_2.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1253" title="ceremony172_2" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/ceremony172_2.png" alt="" width="873" height="466" /></a></p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/abdulrehmceremonyBest.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1252" title="abdulrehmceremonyBest" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/abdulrehmceremonyBest.png" alt="" width="469" height="293" /></a></p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/EkoArt-title.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-419" title="EkoArt title" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/EkoArt-title.png" alt="" width="250" height="90" /></a></p>
<p>I don’t know if she will have time for everyone, but here is an awesome Dancing original eko inspired drawing of LadyGagaLuva! Please share YOUR incredible Eko Art with us at the blog: <a href="mailto:usa_blog@ekoloko.com">usa_blog@ekoloko.com</a>!</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/LadyGagaLuva-by-Dancing.jpg" ><img class="alignnone  wp-image-1256" title="LadyGagaLuva by Dancing" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/LadyGagaLuva-by-Dancing.jpg" alt="" width="209" height="326" /></a></p>
 <div class="clear"> </div>
 <div class="up-bottom-border">
 <p class="postmetadata">Posted in <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=8" title="View all posts in Contests" rel="category">Contests</a>, <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=11" title="View all posts in EkoArt" rel="category">EkoArt</a>, <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=6" title="View all posts in Events" rel="category">Events</a>, <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=7" title="View all posts in Rangers" rel="category">Rangers</a> |   <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?p=1223#comments" title="Comment on Lovely Houses Lovely Days">16 Comments &#187;</a> </p>
 </div>
 </div></div>
 
 <div class="post-1201 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-ekoart category-events category-lokostyle category-rangers" id="post-1201">
 <p class="postmetadataw">Posted by: <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?author=1" title="Posts by admin" rel="author">admin</a> | on February 13, 2013</p>		
 <h2 class="post-title"><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?p=1201">Hearts and Rangers</a></h2>
 <div class="content-ver-sep"> </div>
 <div class="entrytext">
  <p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/love-events-title.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1148" title="love events title" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/love-events-title.png" alt="" width="264" height="90" /></a></p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/valentines-day-party.png" ><img class="alignleft  wp-image-1202" title="valentines day party" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/valentines-day-party.png" alt="" width="123" height="175" /></a>Hope you logged in today, February 13<sup>th</sup>, because today’s special gift will allow you to enter our super misty Valentine’s Day PARTAY! So make sure to get your flashing red star necklace and join in the Valentine’s Day fun! The necklace will be yours for one week, so get your dancing shoes ready!</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>Anyone who has not yet sent in their lovely moon house for the Valentine’s Day moon house competition, please make sure to send it by Sunday the 17<sup>th</sup>! Remember the address? It’s <a href="mailto:usa_blog@ekoloko.com">usa_blog@ekoloko.com</a>!</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/style-title2.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-254" title="style title2" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/style-title2.png" alt="" width="321" height="67" /></a></p>
<p>What are Ekos wearing this week? Their cloaks, of course! In honor of Valentine’s Day, make sure to put on your loveliest outfits and share the love!</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/cloaks1.png" ><img class="wp-image-1204 alignnone" title="cloaks1" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/cloaks1.png" alt="" width="337" height="198" /></a> <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/cloaks2.png" ><img class="alignnone  wp-image-1203" title="cloaks2" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/cloaks2.png" alt="" width="284" height="183" /></a></p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/rangers-of-the-week-header.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-14" title="rangers of the week header" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/rangers-of-the-week-header.png" alt="" width="625" height="62" /></a></p>
<p>Our last Ranger ceremony was sooo exciting and we are very happy to announce our next group of Rangers of the Week!</p>
<p>So without further delay, here they are, by popular demand, your newest soon-to-be Advanced Rangers:  <strong>bouba57, Ramzanahmed, in15na, vikisosa, childofpira and misheli!</strong></p>
<p>Congratulations to our new rangers and continue to make us proud!</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/group7squad2rangers.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1205" title="group7squad2rangers" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/group7squad2rangers.png" alt="" width="558" height="160" /></a></p>
<p>And here is the schedule for the upcoming Ranger ceremonies:</p>
<p><span style="color: #ff00ff;">Sunday, February 17<sup>th</sup>, at 2 PM EST (8 PM France, 9 PM Israel)!</span></p>
<p>For those users who got special permission to have their ceremonies at a different time, please check what time was given to you.</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/EkoArt-title.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-419" title="EkoArt title" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/EkoArt-title.png" alt="" width="250" height="90" /></a></p>
<p>Valentine’s Day has generated a lot of Eko-inspired art…here is another comic strip for your enjoyment – this time from our very own Avrila!</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/Valentines-Day-avrila-comics.png" ><img class="alignnone  wp-image-1211" title="Valentine's Day avrila comics" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/Valentines-Day-avrila-comics.png" alt="" width="515" height="309" /></a></p>
<p>Share your art with us at <a href="mailto:usa_blog@ekoloko.com">usa_blog@ekoloko.com</a>!</p>
<p>And congratulations to Jasper and Dancing for guessing correctly that these lumps in the picture are parked cars covered in snow! The little things sticking out are their side mirrors!</p>
<p>Keep checking back for more fun quizzes!</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/blizzard3.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1188" title="blizzard3" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/blizzard3.png" alt="" width="736" height="474" /></a></p>
 <div class="clear"> </div>
 <div class="up-bottom-border">
 <p class="postmetadata">Posted in <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=11" title="View all posts in EkoArt" rel="category">EkoArt</a>, <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=6" title="View all posts in Events" rel="category">Events</a>, <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=5" title="View all posts in LokoStyle" rel="category">LokoStyle</a>, <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=7" title="View all posts in Rangers" rel="category">Rangers</a> |   <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?p=1201#comments" title="Comment on Hearts and Rangers">13 Comments &#187;</a> </p>
 </div>
 </div></div>
 
 <div class="post-1168 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-donuts category-ekoart category-ekonews category-events category-rangers" id="post-1168">
 <p class="postmetadataw">Posted by: <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?author=1" title="Posts by admin" rel="author">admin</a> | on February 11, 2013</p>		
 <h2 class="post-title"><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?p=1168">Every Day&#8217;s a Rare Day</a></h2>
 <div class="content-ver-sep"> </div>
 <div class="entrytext">
  <p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/love-events-title.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1148" title="love events title" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/love-events-title.png" alt="" width="264" height="90" /></a></p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/happy-valentines.png" ><img class="alignleft  wp-image-1169" title="happy valentines" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/happy-valentines.png" alt="" width="261" height="266" /></a>This is a reminder to continue working on your moon houses and submit them to the Lovely Moon House Valentine’s Day competition.</p>
<p style="text-align: left;">Send it to <a href="mailto:usa_blog@ekoloko.com">usa_blog@ekoloko.com</a>.</p>
<p style="text-align: left;">Tomorrow we officially begin the Valentine’s Day Community Event and it’s going to be LOVELY!  Join the games, donate your Kokos and help ekoloko share the love!</p>
<p style="text-align: left;"><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/love-ekoloko.jpg" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1192" title="love ekoloko" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/love-ekoloko.jpg" alt="" width="586" height="340" /></a></p>
<p style="text-align: left;"><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/rangers-of-the-week-header.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-14" title="rangers of the week header" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/rangers-of-the-week-header.png" alt="" width="625" height="62" /></a></p>
<p>This week’s Advanced Ranger ceremony was PACKED!</p>
<p>In addition to our scheduled amiyoy7, Banana, Rawrcinnamon, Koksiboy and PrincessRawr we also had 1aviv1 and PikachuStyle!!! So many rangers, so much fun!</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/feb10.png" ><img class="alignnone  wp-image-1183" title="feb10" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/feb10.png" alt="" width="700" height="382" /></a></p>
<p>We also had a few visitors – some of whom could not stop talking!!!! (Omriliz, Taleko!) I hope you behave better at your Ranger meetings, or some heads are going to roll!</p>
<p>All in all it was great fun and very exciting to see all of these new Rangers take the pledge and get their halos.</p>
<p>Want to get YOUR Advanced Ranger halo? Finish your Green Ranger quests, and be a GREAT Green Ranger, helpful, kind and friendly, and our managers will consider recommending you to become part of our Advanced Ranger squad. Ekoloko needs you!</p>
<p>The next group of Rangers of the Week will be announced in a few days so come back and check!</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/EkoArt-title.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-419" title="EkoArt title" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/EkoArt-title.png" alt="" width="250" height="90" /></a></p>
<p>What is the most popular activity on ekoloko? What do you think???? Trading. Trading. Trading. Trading. Trading!</p>
<p>Cchen222 has a message for all you Ekos out there that are busy searching for RARE items!</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/not-about-the-rares.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1170" title="not about the rares" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/not-about-the-rares.png" alt="" width="600" height="388" /></a></p>
<p>So listen to Chen and to 1stLady – YOU are ALL rare, to us…even if you only have the clothes you got when you joined. We love you all. We are happy to have you all here. And as Chen wrote, it’s not just about the rares! We are all one big family and we are glad you are a part of it!</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/news-title11.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-120" title="news title1" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/news-title11.png" alt="" width="339" height="63" /></a></p>
<p>So we all thought the snow had ended – on ekoloko and in general…the sun was shining and the days were warming up…and then….BLIZZARD!!!!</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/blizzard1.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1190" title="blizzard1" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/blizzard1.png" alt="" width="754" height="517" /></a></p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/blizzard2.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1189" title="blizzard2" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/blizzard2.png" alt="" width="763" height="379" /></a></p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/blizzard4.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1187" title="blizzard4" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/blizzard4.png" alt="" width="701" height="464" /></a></p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/blizzard3.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1188" title="blizzard3" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/blizzard3.png" alt="" width="736" height="474" /></a></p>
<p>This last picture is my favorite – can you guess what’s in the picture? All correct guesses today (February 11<sup>th</sup>) will win 250 Kokos!</p>
<p>And speaking of snow, get ready because it’s…</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/donuts-corner.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-746" title="donuts corner" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/donuts-corner.png" alt="" width="327" height="67" /></a></p>
<p>Donuts was given some of the new winter potions to try out and give her opinion and here is what she had to say!</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/PotionsComics.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1171" title="PotionsComics" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/PotionsComics.png" alt="" width="800" height="764" /></a></p>
<p>Pick up your potions in the ekoloko MALL!</p>
 <div class="clear"> </div>
 <div class="up-bottom-border">
 <p class="postmetadata">Posted in <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=14" title="View all posts in Donuts" rel="category">Donuts</a>, <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=11" title="View all posts in EkoArt" rel="category">EkoArt</a>, <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=3" title="View all posts in EkoNews" rel="category">EkoNews</a>, <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=6" title="View all posts in Events" rel="category">Events</a>, <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=7" title="View all posts in Rangers" rel="category">Rangers</a> |   <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?p=1168#comments" title="Comment on Every Day&#8217;s a Rare Day">8 Comments &#187;</a> </p>
 </div>
 </div></div>
 
 <div class="post-1158 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-contests category-ekoart category-events category-rangers" id="post-1158">
 <p class="postmetadataw">Posted by: <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?author=1" title="Posts by admin" rel="author">admin</a> | on February 5, 2013</p>		
 <h2 class="post-title"><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?p=1158">Lovely Event</a></h2>
 <div class="content-ver-sep"> </div>
 <div class="entrytext">
  <p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/love-events-title.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1148" title="love events title" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/love-events-title.png" alt="" width="264" height="90" /></a></p>
<p>So many of you have already started sending in your lovely moon  houses and so I thought I’d better get moving and give you the instructions for what to do and how to submit.</p>
<p>So here we go: in honor of the holiday of LOVE, Valentine’s Day, we will be holding a <span style="color: #ff00ff;"><strong>LOVELY MOON HOUSE </strong></span>competition – you need to decorate your moon house inspired by Valentine’s Day (colors, shapes, messages, etc.).</p>
<p>ALL Ekos can participate in the competition. In order to ensure that ALL of the managers get to see your moon houses and know that you are participating – please send a PICTURE of your moon house, and make sure YOU are in it, and that your name is clearly visible. Send it to <a href="mailto:usa_blog@ekoloko.com">usa_blog@ekoloko.com</a>.</p>
<p>The competition will continue UNTIL February 17<sup>th</sup> and winners will be announced on February 18<sup>th</sup> – the last day of the Valentine’s Day Community Event. The managers will continue to visit houses during their shifts until the 17<sup>th</sup> and ANYONE who wants to participate in the contest must make sure to send us (or ask a manager when they are visiting) a picture of your house <span style="color: #ff0000;"><strong>ON OR BEFORE</strong></span> February 17<sup>th</sup>.</p>
<p>We will have 9 winners in total – each manager will get to pick their TOP 3. The prize is…well, let’s leave THAT a surprise!</p>
<p>Good luck and be <span style="color: #ff00ff;">LOVELY</span>!</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/rangers-of-the-week-header.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-14" title="rangers of the week header" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/rangers-of-the-week-header.png" alt="" width="625" height="62" /></a></p>
<p>This week’s group of Fire Halo winners is an interesting mix and a couple of RAWRs!!!</p>
<p>Congratulations to our newest Rangers of the week:</p>
<p>amiyoy7, banana, Rawrcinnamon, abdulrehm745, Koksiboy and PrincessRawr!!!</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/group6squad2rangers.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1159" title="group6squad2rangers" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/group6squad2rangers.png" alt="" width="603" height="261" /></a></p>
<p>Your Advanced Ranger ceremony will take place on Sunday, February 10<sup>th</sup>, at 2 PM Eastern Time (that is 8 PM in France and 21:00 in Israel). The more the merrier – so please mark down the date and time and make sure you’re not late!</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/EkoArt-title.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-419" title="EkoArt title" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/EkoArt-title.png" alt="" width="250" height="90" /></a></p>
<p>Oh I can’t wait until we finally get a blog – because then we’ll be able to have…..SIGNATURES!</p>
<p>Check out this adorable signature sagi9949 created for Megara! Send your original eko-inspired art to <a href="mailto:usa_blog@ekoloko.com">usa_blog@ekoloko.com</a>!</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/Megs-name-art-work.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1161" title="Meg's name art work" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/Megs-name-art-work.png" alt="" width="1366" height="768" /></a></p>
 <div class="clear"> </div>
 <div class="up-bottom-border">
 <p class="postmetadata">Posted in <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=8" title="View all posts in Contests" rel="category">Contests</a>, <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=11" title="View all posts in EkoArt" rel="category">EkoArt</a>, <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=6" title="View all posts in Events" rel="category">Events</a>, <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=7" title="View all posts in Rangers" rel="category">Rangers</a> |   <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?p=1158#comments" title="Comment on Lovely Event">13 Comments &#187;</a> </p>
 </div>
 </div></div>
 
 <div class="post-1144 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-ekoart category-events category-rangers" id="post-1144">
 <p class="postmetadataw">Posted by: <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?author=1" title="Posts by admin" rel="author">admin</a> | on February 4, 2013</p>		
 <h2 class="post-title"><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?p=1144">OMG I Forgot!</a></h2>
 <div class="content-ver-sep"> </div>
 <div class="entrytext">
  <p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/rangers-of-the-week-header.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-14" title="rangers of the week header" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/rangers-of-the-week-header.png" alt="" width="625" height="62" /></a></p>
<p>A BIG apology goes to Ofeky123, LeBron and Silverdragon!!! Ofeky – you were right…and here it is &#8212;- the missing Ranger Ceremony picture!!!</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/jan613.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1146" title="jan613" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/jan613.png" alt="" width="864" height="431" /></a></p>
<p>So sorry you guys—especially since it was such a FUN ceremony … I guess you should make me walk the plank, aye mateys? !</p>
<p>Yesterday we had a HUGE ceremony for ONE Eko: congratulations XTREME!</p>
<p>1aviv1 DID eventually show up (one hour late – bad boy!!!) and will now have his ceremony next week, together with our other NO-SHOWS and our new advanced rangers, who will be announced later this week.</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/xtremes-ceremony.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1145" title="xtremes ceremony" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/xtremes-ceremony.png" alt="" width="905" height="471" /></a></p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/EkoArt-title.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-419" title="EkoArt title" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/EkoArt-title.png" alt="" width="250" height="90" /></a></p>
<p>Once again it is time to pop some popcorn and sit back to enjoy another wonderful music video clip – this one was created by Omriliz and friends: missions, donuts, taleko, dancing, butterfly, yuvalXD and special guest appearance by hazuzu!</p>
<p style="text-align: left;" dir="RTL" align="right"><a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=p61XJUhiD2c" onclick="javascript:_gaq.push(['_trackEvent','outbound-article','http://www.youtube.com']);">http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=p61XJUhiD2c</a></p>
<p>I’m loving it! How about you?</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/love-events-title.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1148" title="love events title" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/love-events-title.png" alt="" width="264" height="90" /></a></p>
<p>And want to know what ELSE I’m loving?</p>
<p>Valentine’s Day, that’s what! Valentine’s Day is the holiday of <span style="color: #ff0000;"><strong>LOVE</strong></span> – and I <span style="color: #ff0000;"><strong>LOVE</strong></span> when all you Ekos come to play on ekoloko! I <span style="color: #ff0000;"><strong>LOVE</strong></span> when you read the blog and send me things and I <span style="color: #ff0000;"><strong>LOVE</strong></span> when you are having fun!</p>
<p>So join us for some <strong><span style="color: #ff0000;">LOVELY</span> FUN</strong> – beginning this weekend and going through Valentine’s Day and ending on the 18<sup>th</sup> of February – when some <span style="color: #ff0000;"><strong>LOVELY</strong></span> Ekos will win a <span style="color: #ff0000;"><strong>LOVELY</strong></span> prize for their <span style="color: #ff0000;"><strong>LOVELY</strong></span> moon homes!</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/load.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1149" title="load" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/load.png" alt="" width="853" height="446" /></a></p>
 <div class="clear"> </div>
 <div class="up-bottom-border">
 <p class="postmetadata">Posted in <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=11" title="View all posts in EkoArt" rel="category">EkoArt</a>, <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=6" title="View all posts in Events" rel="category">Events</a>, <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=7" title="View all posts in Rangers" rel="category">Rangers</a> |   <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?p=1144#comments" title="Comment on OMG I Forgot!">10 Comments &#187;</a> </p>
 </div>
 </div></div>
 
 <div class="post-1123 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-contests category-ekoart category-ekonews category-events" id="post-1123">
 <p class="postmetadataw">Posted by: <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?author=1" title="Posts by admin" rel="author">admin</a> | on January 31, 2013</p>		
 <h2 class="post-title"><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?p=1123">Snow Potion Fun</a></h2>
 <div class="content-ver-sep"> </div>
 <div class="entrytext">
  <p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/football-event-title.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1105" title="football event title" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/football-event-title.png" alt="" width="250" height="96" /></a></p>
<p>Tomorrow it begins! Our weekend special in honor of that difficult-to-understand sport: American football!!!</p>
<p>If any of you out there understand this game – and I’m from NY and I STILL don’t get it!!! – please send us your explanation of American football, and I’ll post it on the blog!!!</p>
<p>Remember the address: <a href="mailto:usa_blog@ekoloko.com">usa_blog@ekoloko.com</a>! Waiting to hear from you!</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/EkoArt-title.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-419" title="EkoArt title" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/EkoArt-title.png" alt="" width="250" height="90" /></a></p>
<p>Look out Dancing! There’s another artist in town! Check out this awesome drawing done by Rona777! Keep sending us your awesome eko-inspired art! I’d love to do some t-shirts with these drawings…</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/by-rona777.png" ><img class="aligncenter  wp-image-1125" title="by rona777" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/by-rona777.png" alt="" width="441" height="455" /></a></p>
<p style="text-align: left;"><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/contests1.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-122" title="contests1" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/contests1.png" alt="" width="312" height="50" /></a></p>
<p>So the response this time wasn’t so great, but of course we have our winners!!!</p>
<p>Here one last time is the original screenshot for our drawing contest this time:</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/original.png" ><img class="alignnone  wp-image-1013" title="original" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/original.png" alt="" width="544" height="324" /></a></p>
<p>And here are our WINNERS!!! Congratulations <strong>Butterfly and Dancing4lyfe</strong>!!!</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/rotem-butterfly.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1126" title="rotem butterfly" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/rotem-butterfly.png" alt="" width="894" height="540" /></a></p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/jessica-dancing.jpg" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1127" title="jessica dancing" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/jessica-dancing.jpg" alt="" width="906" height="540" /></a></p>
<p>Coming soon!!! New design contests! So get ready!!!</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/news-title1.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-13" title="news title1" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/news-title1.png" alt="" width="349" height="104" /></a></p>
<p>Have you tried out the new potions yet??? <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/GreatEkolokoSnowman.jpg" ><img class="alignright  wp-image-1131" title="GreatEkolokoSnowman" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/GreatEkolokoSnowman.jpg" alt="" width="382" height="341" /></a>Get them while they last at the ekoloko MALL!</p>
<p>Who are the 3 snowmen hiding in this scene? Guess all 3 and you&#8217;ll win ekoCoins to purchase this cool potion!!!</p>
 <div class="clear"> </div>
 <div class="up-bottom-border">
 <p class="postmetadata">Posted in <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=8" title="View all posts in Contests" rel="category">Contests</a>, <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=11" title="View all posts in EkoArt" rel="category">EkoArt</a>, <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=3" title="View all posts in EkoNews" rel="category">EkoNews</a>, <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=6" title="View all posts in Events" rel="category">Events</a> |   <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?p=1123#comments" title="Comment on Snow Potion Fun">34 Comments &#187;</a> </p>
 </div>
 </div></div>
 
 <div class="post-1100 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-ekonews category-events category-rangers" id="post-1100">
 <p class="postmetadataw">Posted by: <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?author=1" title="Posts by admin" rel="author">admin</a> | on January 29, 2013</p>		
 <h2 class="post-title"><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?p=1100">Kick Offs</a></h2>
 <div class="content-ver-sep"> </div>
 <div class="entrytext">
  <p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/football-event-title.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1105" title="football event title" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/football-event-title.png" alt="" width="250" height="96" /></a></p>
<p>Who doesn’t love FOOTBALL???! <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/football.png" ><img class="alignright size-full wp-image-1106" title="football" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/football.png" alt="" width="345" height="264" /></a>And we’re not talking soccer, but good ole’ American FOOTBALL – the slamming, ramming, getting muddy kind!</p>
<p>This weekend join us for some sporty FOOTBALL FUN as we KICK OFF the weekend with a tribute to the SUPERBOWL!</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/loader1.png" ><img class="aligncenter  wp-image-1104" title="loader" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/loader1.png" alt="" width="687" height="337" /></a></p>
<p style="text-align: left;"><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/rangers-of-the-week-header.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-14" title="rangers of the week header" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/rangers-of-the-week-header.png" alt="" width="625" height="62" /></a></p>
<p>This week we held 2 small ranger ceremonies for Ekos who couldn’t get to their scheduled meetings…Did I say small??? There was STANDING ROOM ONLY!</p>
<p>Congratulations to our new halo’d Advanced Rangers: mami41 and Rose813!!!</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/ceremony271_4.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1102" title="ceremony271_4" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/ceremony271_4.png" alt="" width="847" height="402" /></a></p>
<p>Mami41’s ceremony had LOTS of spectators showing off their spring fashions and enjoying the fun potion party that followed the ceremony. Even the dino cubs got into the act. Hey, has anyone else noticed that the triceratops bodies are a different color than their heads???</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/ceremonyRose813.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1101" title="ceremonyRose813" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/ceremonyRose813.png" alt="" width="830" height="460" /></a></p>
<p>Rose813 had a smaller yet still quality ceremony where she solemnly promised to be the best ranger she could possibly be!</p>
<p>And of course…what you’ve all been waiting for: the next group of rangers who have qualified to join our Advanced Ranger squad!</p>
<p><strong>Congratulations to</strong>: 1aviv1, XTREME, PikachuStyle, Rajveer and EkoIokoEko!!!!!</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/group5squad2rangers.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1103" title="group5squad2rangers" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/group5squad2rangers.png" alt="" width="606" height="271" /></a></p>
<p>Your ranger ceremony will be next Sunday at 2 PM Eastern Time (that’s NY time). For France, that’s 8 PM and in Israel that’s 9 PM. See you there!</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/news-title1.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-13" title="news title1" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/news-title1.png" alt="" width="349" height="104" /></a></p>
<p>What’s new on ekoloko? New items in the MALL – that’s what!!!<a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/new-items-in-mall.png" ><img class="alignright  wp-image-1115" title="new items in mall" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/new-items-in-mall.png" alt="" width="600" height="368" /></a></p>
<p>Here are some of the new items available now at the ekoloko MALL!</p>
<p>Check them out and more and get ready for the cool weather!</p>
<p>And OMG, don’t forget to pick up some of those awesome new potions…they are sooooooooooooo FUNNY!</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/new-potions.png" ><img class="alignleft  wp-image-1114" title="new potions" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/new-potions.png" alt="" width="202" height="174" /></a><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/new-potions1.png" ><img class="alignright size-full wp-image-1118" title="new potions1" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/new-potions1.png" alt="" width="169" height="145" /></a></p>
 <div class="clear"> </div>
 <div class="up-bottom-border">
 <p class="postmetadata">Posted in <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=3" title="View all posts in EkoNews" rel="category">EkoNews</a>, <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=6" title="View all posts in Events" rel="category">Events</a>, <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=7" title="View all posts in Rangers" rel="category">Rangers</a> |   <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?p=1100#comments" title="Comment on Kick Offs">18 Comments &#187;</a> </p>
 </div>
 </div></div>
 
 <div class="post-1075 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-contests category-ekoart category-ekonews" id="post-1075">
 <p class="postmetadataw">Posted by: <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?author=1" title="Posts by admin" rel="author">admin</a> | on January 27, 2013</p>		
 <h2 class="post-title"><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?p=1075">Waving Hands and Hand Man</a></h2>
 <div class="content-ver-sep"> </div>
 <div class="entrytext">
  <p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/contests1.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-122" title="contests1" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/contests1.png" alt="" width="312" height="50" /></a></p>
<p>So it looks like Pollux’s Hand Man Competition was a huge success, and in his honor, we will be making this a regular activity on ekoloko USA – at least once a month, maybe more often. So if you didn’t win this time – there’s always NEXT time! Make sure to check the blog for information and ask the managers!</p>
<p><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Here are the winners from the FINALS for the Pollux Hand Man Tournament!!!  </span></strong></p>
<p>FIRST PLACE: <strong>Liluna</strong> (GOLD MEDAL!)</p>
<p>SECOND PLACE: Tie between <strong>hadaror</strong> and <strong>migo71 </strong>(SILVER MEDAL!)</p>
<p>THIRD PLACE: Tie between <strong>Dancing4Lyfe</strong> and <strong>Riki07 </strong>(BRONZE MEDAL!)</p>
<p><strong>CONGRATULATIONS TO ALL THE WINNERS!!!!</strong></p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/Finals.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1076" title="Finals" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/Finals.png" alt="" width="782" height="490" /></a></p>
<p>And speaking of CONTESTS…so far I have 2 winners in the screen design contest, but there’s still time to submit YOUR original version of Pierre Milkyway’s galactic restaurant….let’s see how original YOU are! Send your drawings to <a href="mailto:usa_blog@ekoloko.com">usa_blog@ekoloko.com</a>!</p>
<p>Once more, here is the original screen for you to design:</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/original.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1013" title="original" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/original.png" alt="" width="906" height="540" /></a></p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/EkoArt-title.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-419" title="EkoArt title" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/EkoArt-title.png" alt="" width="250" height="90" /></a></p>
<p>OMG!!! Another awesome drawing from Dancing4Lyfe!!! I already told her I thought she should go to ART SCHOOL.</p>
<p><img class="wp-image-1080 alignright" title="megara by dancing" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/megara-by-dancing.jpg" alt="" width="293" height="425" /></p>
<p>What do YOU think? Somebody buy that girl more paper and colored pencils because folks will be lining up for her drawings! Girl, you&#8217;ve got talent!</p>
<p>This, by the way, is Dancing&#8217;s view of Megara!</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/message-from-title.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-860" title="message from title" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/message-from-title.png" alt="" width="301" height="59" /></a></p>
<p>As you may have heard, we are saying goodbye to some of our managers who have gone off to do other things, while we put all our efforts into a few special projects that are taking some extra energy.</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/1stLady_101612.png" ><img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-863" title="1stLady_101612" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/1stLady_101612.png" alt="" width="156" height="323" /></a>We are all very sad to say goodbye to NailGaga, Hazuzu and Pollux – they each had their own way of making all of us Ekos and Managers alike feel special and loved. They were fun, funny and had a way with words and potions!</p>
<p>We will all miss them and look forward to seeing them again very soon! So let’s not say ‘goodbye’ – let’s say ‘Au revoir’ as our French friends say – which means, until we see each other again!</p>
<p>Now it is time to look forward – we have some amazing new things we are working on that will be ready soon…and although it will be hard for Megara and IzzyRo with just me to help them play with all the Ekos…we all believe that this effort will be worth it.</p>
<p>And finally, here’s a special request to all our Rangers out there – now is a time not to think of leaving…now is a time to come even more and show us that we were right to make you Rangers. Fulfill your roles and help us help new Ekos, bring more friends and help everyone learn about ekoloko and all the different ways to have fun here. You took a pledge, and we need you now more than ever. <strong>Make us proud!</strong></p>
 <div class="clear"> </div>
 <div class="up-bottom-border">
 <p class="postmetadata">Posted in <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=8" title="View all posts in Contests" rel="category">Contests</a>, <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=11" title="View all posts in EkoArt" rel="category">EkoArt</a>, <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=3" title="View all posts in EkoNews" rel="category">EkoNews</a> |   <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?p=1075#comments" title="Comment on Waving Hands and Hand Man">27 Comments &#187;</a> </p>
 </div>
 </div></div>
 
 <div class="post-1058 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-contests category-donuts category-ekoart" id="post-1058">
 <p class="postmetadataw">Posted by: <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?author=1" title="Posts by admin" rel="author">admin</a> | on January 26, 2013</p>		
 <h2 class="post-title"><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?p=1058">A Donut in the Hand is Worth 2</a></h2>
 <div class="content-ver-sep"> </div>
 <div class="entrytext">
  <p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/contests1.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-122" title="contests1" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/contests1.png" alt="" width="312" height="50" /></a></p>
<p><strong>So you think you&#8217;re a master at Hand Man?</strong></p>
<p><strong>Join Pollux for a special two-day Hand Man competition!</strong></p>
<p><strong>Amazing prizes will be awarded to the 1st, 2nd, and 3rd place winners from the FINAL game!</strong></p>
<p><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Here are the winners from the opening games on Friday!!!  </span></strong></p>
<p><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;">All of you will participate in the Semi-Finals on Sunday, starting at 10 a.m. Eastern (NY) time. That is 5 p.m. (17:00) in Israel, and 4 p.m. (16:00) in France.</span></strong></p>
<p>Liluna<br />
XTREME<br />
Dancing4lyfe<br />
noam1991<br />
matan078<br />
Taleko<br />
gobogo<br />
yuvalXD<br />
Omriliz<br />
butterfly<br />
fionadawn<br />
FirstEko<br />
in15na</p>
<p>Couldn’t make it to the opening games on Friday??? You still have a chance! There is one more opening game on Sunday:</p>
<p>Opening Game Three &#8212; Sunday, January 27th, 9 AM Eastern Time (16:00 Israel, 15:00 France)</p>
<p>Semi-Final Game One &#8212; Sunday, January 27th, 10 AM Eastern Time</p>
<p>Semi-Final Game Two &#8212; Sunday, January 27th, 11AM Eastern Time (if needed)</p>
<p><strong>FINAL GAME &#8212; Sunday, January 27th, 12PM Eastern Time (19:00 Israel, 18:00 France)</strong></p>
<p><strong>ALL GAMES WILL BE HELD IN RAINBOW SHUTTLE, JUNGLE, SERVER 2!!!</strong></p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Here again are the rules:</span></p>
<p>You may play in ONE opening game.</p>
<p>If Pollux announces you as a winner of your game you can then compete in another game.</p>
<p>Opening game winners will participate in the Semi-Final game(s).</p>
<p>All Semi-Final game winners must attend the Final game. Players must be on time to participate in the Final Game. We cannot change the time of any games.</p>
<p>Spectators welcome!!!</p>
<p><strong>Remember: Amazing prizes will be awarded for 1<sup>st</sup>, 2<sup>nd</sup> and 3<sup>rd</sup> place winners in the Finals!</strong></p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/Big-game-opening-hand-man.png" ><img class="alignnone  wp-image-1061" title="Big game opening hand man" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/Big-game-opening-hand-man.png" alt="" width="624" height="385" /></a></p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/hand-man-2.png" ><img class="alignnone  wp-image-1062" title="hand man (2)" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/hand-man-2.png" alt="" width="576" height="295" /></a></p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/EkoArt-title.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-419" title="EkoArt title" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/EkoArt-title.png" alt="" width="250" height="90" /></a></p>
<p>Here is a cool idea – and we’d love to see more of your original ideas (hey, what about those screen designs????) – NOBODY has sent in a screen so I guess you didn’t like the original??? Boo hoo…hope someone tries to win.<a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/Faces.png" ><img class="alignright size-full wp-image-1065" title="Faces" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/Faces.png" alt="" width="467" height="266" /></a></p>
<p>Anyway – here is Dancing’s cute screen demonstrating the different faces of ekoloko! You can make a face too – just press the 1-2-3-4-5 keys!</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/donuts-corner.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-746" title="donuts corner" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/donuts-corner.png" alt="" width="327" height="67" /></a></p>
<p>I know…you’ve been wondering, and waiting, and hoping she’d find time…and she has…here is another in a series of wonderful comics about WHAT’S HAPPENING EKOLOKO!!!!</p>
<p>Woo hoo! Thanks Donuts…and congrats on the great grades in English!!!!! We’re so proud!</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/Boomerang-Commando.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1069" title="Boomerang-Commando" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/Boomerang-Commando.png" alt="" width="800" height="578" /></a></p>
<p>Have any of YOU tried this new game? Tell us what you think of it! We&#8217;d love to hear your comments!!! Post them to the blog.</p>
 <div class="clear"> </div>
 <div class="up-bottom-border">
 <p class="postmetadata">Posted in <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=8" title="View all posts in Contests" rel="category">Contests</a>, <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=14" title="View all posts in Donuts" rel="category">Donuts</a>, <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=11" title="View all posts in EkoArt" rel="category">EkoArt</a> |   <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?p=1058#comments" title="Comment on A Donut in the Hand is Worth 2">17 Comments &#187;</a> </p>
 </div>
 </div></div>
 
 
